results.title: Pet Food | FDA
results.explanation: The article discusses the regulations for pet food, including canned pet foods (21 CFR 113), and states that contamination or spoilage could prevent cats from consuming pet food. The issue of cats not returning to affected cans later and their unimpressed looks can be interpreted as possible signs of contamination or spoilage.
